\frametitle{JAGS: computing with automatic Gibbs sampling}
\begin{itemize}
\item JAGS (Just Another Gibbs Sampler) is a stand alone software package for automatic Gibbs sampling.
\item It has a convenient R interface package {\tt rjags}, which in turn interfaces readily with the {\tt coda} R package for MCMC diagnostics.
\item See \verb+http://mcmc-jags.sourceforge.net/+ to get your own copy of JAGS.
\item \verb+install.packages("rjags")+ to install {\tt rjags} in R.
\end{itemize}
